'''Mantilorrian rat-catchers''' were entities originating in the [[Mantilorr system/Legends|Mantilorr system]]. Some of them were employed by [[Kwenn Space Station/Legends|Kwenn Space Station]]. Mantilorrian rat-catchers attempted to capture the [[Kowakian monkey-lizard/Legends|Kowakian monkey-lizard]] [[Salacious B. Crumb/Legends|Salacious B. Crumb]] when he became too much of a pest aboard the station.

